	(text_box "About:\n- Buck converter generates 3.3V out of 4-35V, output up to 500mA. By defult, power converter is off and whole system too. To enable it, signal from outside WAKE_UP needs to be set to 1. After that, once STM32 controller gets on, it can continue keeping power on by setting PWR_ON signal to 1."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
